‚ĖĀThe ‚ĖĀauthors ‚ĖĀsay ‚ĖĀthat ‚ĖĀwhen ‚ĖĀthe ‚ĖĀSARS ‚ĖĀoutbreak ‚ĖĀbegan ‚ĖĀin ‚ĖĀ2002, ‚ĖĀChina ‚ĖĀwas ‚ĖĀinitially ‚ĖĀill - p repared , ‚ĖĀespecially ‚ĖĀfor ‚ĖĀpath ogens .
