‚ĖĀSecond , ‚ĖĀwith ‚ĖĀthe ‚ĖĀexception ‚ĖĀof ‚ĖĀdangerous ‚ĖĀchemicals , ‚ĖĀon - the - ground ‚ĖĀreviews ‚ĖĀof ‚ĖĀproducts ‚ĖĀlicens ed ‚ĖĀby ‚ĖĀprovincial - level ‚ĖĀPeople ‚Äô s ‚ĖĀGovernment ‚ĖĀQ ual ity ‚ĖĀTechnology ‚ĖĀSup erv ision ‚ĖĀ( the ‚ĖĀmarket - s up erv ision ‚ĖĀauthority ), ‚ĖĀcompanies ‚ĖĀsubmitted ‚ĖĀqualified ‚ĖĀreporting ‚ĖĀon ‚ĖĀapplic ants ‚ĖĀand ‚ĖĀproduct ‚ĖĀtests , ‚ĖĀand ‚ĖĀissued ‚ĖĀcommitments ‚ĖĀguaranteeing ‚ĖĀquality - quality ‚ĖĀreporting , ‚ĖĀwhich ‚ĖĀwere ‚ĖĀproperly ‚ĖĀve t ested ‚ĖĀto ‚ĖĀreceive ‚ĖĀlic enses , ‚ĖĀand ‚ĖĀthen ‚ĖĀsubject ‚ĖĀto ‚ĖĀin - person ‚ĖĀreviews ‚ĖĀover ‚ĖĀtime .
