‚ĖĀThe ‚ĖĀresolution ‚ĖĀdemands ‚ĖĀthat ‚ĖĀall ‚ĖĀregions , ‚ĖĀrelevant ‚ĖĀministries ‚ĖĀfollow ‚ĖĀthrough ‚ĖĀon ‚ĖĀtheir ‚ĖĀefforts ‚ĖĀto ‚ĖĀsuppress ‚ĖĀthe ‚ĖĀrecords ‚ĖĀand ‚ĖĀstream line ‚ĖĀapproval ‚ĖĀprocesses .
‚ĖĀIncreas ing ‚ĖĀcompanies ‚Äô ‚ĖĀcommitment ‚ĖĀto ‚ĖĀpublic ‚ĖĀand ‚ĖĀback - lo aded ‚ĖĀcensorship , ‚ĖĀstrengthening ‚ĖĀcredit ‚ĖĀmonitoring ‚ĖĀand ‚ĖĀconstraints , ‚ĖĀenforcing ‚ĖĀaccountability ‚ĖĀfor ‚ĖĀquality ‚ĖĀactors , ‚ĖĀand ‚ĖĀrev oking ‚ĖĀthe ‚ĖĀlicens ing ‚ĖĀpermits ‚ĖĀof ‚ĖĀproduction ‚ĖĀon ‚ĖĀfalse ‚ĖĀcommitments , ‚ĖĀas ‚ĖĀrequ ested .
‚ĖĀTo ‚ĖĀenforce ‚ĖĀregulations ‚ĖĀon ‚ĖĀproducts ‚ĖĀlike ‚ĖĀpublic ‚ĖĀhealth ‚ĖĀand ‚ĖĀsafety , ‚ĖĀenvironmental ‚ĖĀprotection , ‚ĖĀlist ing ‚ĖĀpositive ‚ĖĀl ists , ‚ĖĀun ifying ‚ĖĀcert ification ‚ĖĀstandards , ‚ĖĀreasonable ‚ĖĀreduction , ‚ĖĀand ‚ĖĀcert ification ‚ĖĀtesting ‚ĖĀprograms , ‚ĖĀmandatory ‚ĖĀbills ‚ĖĀare , ‚ĖĀin ‚ĖĀprinciple , ‚ĖĀsubject ‚ĖĀto ‚ĖĀinstitutional ‚ĖĀobligations ‚ĖĀat ‚ĖĀall ‚ĖĀlevels .
‚ĖĀAd op ting ‚ĖĀsupport ‚ĖĀmeasures ‚ĖĀto ‚ĖĀencourage ‚ĖĀvoluntary ‚ĖĀcert ification ‚ĖĀby ‚ĖĀcorporations , ‚ĖĀand ‚ĖĀto ‚ĖĀpromote ‚ĖĀbrand ing ‚ĖĀand ‚ĖĀexpand ‚ĖĀthe ‚ĖĀmarket .
